/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"that drive\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone in the gym is constantly pushing each other to be better.\\\"\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan credits her ascendancy during the abridged three-year cycle since Tokyo to the inspiration she gleaned from being up close and personal in the Japanese capital, whereCook fell to a narrow semi-final defeatand had to rouse herself to win a bronze medal for the second straight Games.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9996483246521144, \"rank\": 0.0002906725727674821, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ascendancy\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the abridged three-year cycle\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"the inspiration\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"whereCook\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"a narrow semi-final defeatand\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the second straight Games\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tokyo was a fire that was lit inside me,\\\" McGowan added.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898962855706287, \"rank\": 0.010206830077974191, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fire\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess I'd accepted that it wasn't going to be my Games, but when I was out there I told myself I'd done the hard part, and I was not going to go through the same thing again in Paris.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999985266186, \"rank\": 1.4731623823601239e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my Games\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard part\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had multiple injuries in this cycle, including an operation on my hip, but despite knowing how tough it was going to be to get there, I believed in myself and with the right mindset I knew I could keep striving for more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple injuries\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"this cycle\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"an operation\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"my hip\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"the right mindset\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan, who grew up in Dumbarton and is the first Scottish athlete to compete in taekwondo at the Olympics, said she had been inspired to follow in the footsteps of the domestic sport's standard bearer, Sarah Stevenson, and Serbian doubleOlympic champion Milica Mandic, whom McGowan beat to clinch her breakthrough European crown in 2021.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9995261467801909, \"rank\": 0.0004740778435951653, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.460384038376809e-11, \"text\": \"Dumbarton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.992391785643348, \"rank\": 0.00462116617576125